師通常都會幫佢取字<br />\n<br />\n我老豆果代已經無，阿爺細過係舉人親戚幫佢取字，我曾太爺果代開始已經無人中進士，慢慢變咗做地主，不過都有取字"},{"pid":"ecea3b0d6803d69d373da740c74fce909d9126e4","tid":884031,"uid":67812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:18:27.000Z","msg":"將來香港滅國，唔好忘記大家都係香氏人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0217c3ba87737ddc3621375161a275bec1494738","tid":884031,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"古人個名多數得一粒字 <br />\n字就兩粒字<br />\n而字又呼應返個名<br />\n低今時今日大家個名都係兩粒字<br />\n兩粒大多都有不同義<br />\n想改過字都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9555903ea2679d94960266a53e546318ec5f13df","tid":884031,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古人個名多數得一粒字 <br />\n字就兩粒字<br />\n而字又呼應返個名<br />\n但今時今日大家個名都係兩粒字<br />\n兩粒大多都有不同義<br />\n想改個字都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f3f60926caf9f71df1e8943442a99c0739df1a1a","tid":884031,"uid":33749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c14f5fc8785807d15e7d6f355ab19606c6314040","tid":884031,"uid":185712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"唔一定要貴族既<br />\n<br />\n讀書人既話，老師通常都會幫佢取字<br />\n<br />\n我老豆果代已經無，阿爺細過係舉人親戚幫佢取字，我曾太爺果代開始已經無人中進士，慢慢變咗做地主，不過都有取字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"我嗰邊係結婚時會改個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老豆嗰輩同我堂哥都有字，不過冇用過，淨係有塊木牌寫住<br />\n我阿爺塊墓碑都係寫佢個字，而唔係寫佢個名，X公AB咁<br />\n嫲嫲就直接寫X門Y氏"},{"pid":"3567b9d9005b81cd030604fd37324380a65ee54b","tid":884031,"uid":83504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"lm學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多學識之人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0338bc5f89c7ae1e350d42414b7f0fb8f12530b5","tid":884031,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"周瑜字公瑾<br />\n自宮緊"},{"pid":"46af88450a277a24d17a637e441231aa97022c5a","tid":884031,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0217c3ba87737ddc3621375161a275bec1494738","tid":884031,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"古人個名多數得一粒字 <br />\n字就兩粒字<br />\n而字又呼應返個名<br />\n低今時今日大家個名都係兩粒字<br />\n兩粒大多都有不同義<br />\n想改過字都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"好似又有啲唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都有唔少古人用兩個字做名<br />\n但佢哋都會係有字"},{"pid":"4350a86649916227a51635449e5e375b81620f87","tid":884031,"uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:25:48.000Z","msg":"字豬西"},{"pid":"9b26387f5defd08c21e10dbd7c4946a525f3f03b","tid":884031,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"陳大明，字 david"},{"pid":"59cc7363c00917e1a91715c045ba1a6ce4ee5a32","tid":884031,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"其實咪即係花名。<br />\n<br />\n宜家都有啊，死肥X，肥X，四眼X，排骨X，淫X。"},{"pid":"e27fc83bdce8840ccea3da024c0afb7e55e4553f","tid":884031,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc9ab2ce07d9d8e9809530c07d8e58e7aeec2fbc","tid":884031,"uid":161418,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"68c435b28b58600a1cea8e009afc215206827b8f","tid":884031,"uid":30478,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"507b480d7f92e3403be6270db91137eed6635ba6","tid":884031,"uid":34760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"類似<br />\n但係氏唔一定係黎自地方<br />\n<br />\n二、出自子姓。西周初期，成湯的後裔微子啟被封於宋國，微子啟死後，其弟宋微仲繼位。微仲九世孫孔父嘉為宋上卿，遭受迫害，他的後代逃到魯國，以其名字中的「孔」為氏，也是子姓孔氏。仲尼（孔子）即是孔父嘉七世孫[2]。<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n貴族獲得氏的方式有：<br />\n<br />\n以國名為氏<br />\n以邑名為氏<br />\n以官名為氏<br />\n以職業名為氏<br />\n以住地之名為氏<br />\n以同周王或侯君主血緣關係遠近之稱為氏<br />\n以貴族的字為氏"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"照咁睇即係&quot;氏&quot;係撻朵既時侯用<br />\n類似 &quot;銅鑼灣陳浩南&quot; / &quot;東星耀揚&quot;?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:12:25.000Z","msg":"笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"離撚哂譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下史記 孔子世家先啦 屌<br />\n<br />\n孟子荀卿墨翟 全部有名架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d個名就有爭議"},{"pid":"78d35fbb9c622c5afad96cb026eb4df17fb9a697","tid":884031,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"你無姐<br />\n<br />\n我姓吳<br />\n<br />\n名彥祖<br />\n<br />\n字夫子"},{"pid":"4d98f4d13c24bef769049cc5f9e427c14c26feed","tid":884031,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"因為宜家有網名 你想改幾多個都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a770ac40379efbc195f70a2f38f40e020de252d3","tid":884031,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:11:25.000Z","msg":"我阿爺都有字啦 咩古時<br />\n字你自己改渣嘛 而家你都可以作個"},{"pid":"a1359c80b09ba976a8c69e91b136e9202fdfdd86","tid":884031,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"124fc55a7c28d1cbf3cef17778f029fafd52471f","tid":884031,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:46:15.000Z","msg":"例如姓關名羽字雲長<br />\n幾時開始係冇左個字?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"你個字咪叫Grayfox囉"},{"pid":"a6bbc71dea12297844f0e8431eae9a57e6ab73f5","tid":884031,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"題外話。<br />\n<br />\n印象中，孔子，字「仲尼」個「仲」字係以家庭兄弟排位嚟命名。伯、仲、叔、季。<br />\n<br />\n春秋戰國時好多人啲名就都有呢四個字係個名度。<br />\n<br />\n所以睇個名就知佢老幾。"},{"pid":"fdafd206cd6e475777906c1ead945b4632873cbd","tid":884031,"uid":12432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6bbc71dea12297844f0e8431eae9a57e6ab73f5","tid":884031,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"題外話。<br />\n<br />\n印象中，孔子，字「仲尼」個「仲」字係以家庭兄弟排位嚟命名。伯、仲、叔、季。<br />\n<br />\n春秋戰國時好多人啲名就都有呢四個字係個名度。<br />\n<br />\n所以睇個名就知佢老幾。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:42:52.000Z","msg":"伯符 仲謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c3c9912c5a7f59518d9181f114c29b8cd269fb","tid":884031,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"姓 = 父系 先人 宗族（財富 權力 地位）<br />\n氏 = 母系 後人 血脈（女人先100%肯定子女系親生既）<br />\n<br />\n例如：戚秦氏<br />\n戚 = 戚家<br />\n秦氏 = 秦國後人"},{"pid":"12353695f3fb856c0580545a614bc0a7e7a4c6d1","tid":884031,"uid":206673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4d87d66e228b79561940876f4f97e78d13ad48a6","tid":884031,"uid":81424,"like":354,"dislike":0,"score":354,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"有姓有氏有名有字有號添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:47:10.000Z","msg":"有你有我有情有生有有死有義添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4493cac7a10ef70831540606a504ed51fa804be0","tid":884031,"uid":119545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"因為身份證張晶片唔夠位儲咁多個字"},{"pid":"a8b77790f8163eeb55e554c6560e3a57fc729529","tid":884031,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74c3c9912c5a7f59518d9181f114c29b8cd269fb","tid":884031,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"姓 = 父系 先人 宗族（財富 權力 地位）<br />\n氏 = 母系 後人 血脈（女人先100%肯定子女系親生既）<br />\n<br />\n例如：戚秦氏<br />\n戚 = 戚家<br />\n秦氏 = 秦國後人"},"citedBy":0,